This game was Wiimm-fi patched to allow online play/interactions even after Nintendo Wi-fi Shutdown. For more info check here: http://wiki.tockdom.com/wiki/Wiimmfi_Project

This torrent contains a Nintendo Wii Game in WBFS format, which is actually just a compressed ISO image that your Wii reads directly from a hard drive via these Usb Loaders: Usb Loader Gx and CFg Loader.
